Invocation Name: quarantine activities
des:
Ask for something to do and discover a way to be productive during quarantine.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Quarantine Activities" or "Alexa, open Quarantine Activities" to get a suggestion.

At any time, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
